%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: NPC_Bear_Dialogue_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: deeb710d6afc5464696faed10a17b111, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 18066821120
    m_Localized: Hey! What?! Huh?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 239404437504
    m_Localized: What's wrong with you? Why would you poke a bear with a tiny stick
      like that?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 380672790528
    m_Localized: You don't look too bright, so I'll give you a pass this time...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 539083264000
    m_Localized: But if you ever do that again I will make sure you regret it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 744268615680
    m_Localized: Right. So you've decided to push your luck, eh?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 874443034624
    m_Localized: This is once, with a first consequence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1045721632768
    m_Localized: It's just an annoyance, but this will not end where you think it
      does.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1187266809856
    m_Localized: I'd keep from using that stick on me in the future.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1394863886336
    m_Localized: Wait, what?!?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2084596207616
    m_Localized: So twice... two times... warned and all?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2183267209216
    m_Localized: Consider this a justified ascension, harsher but palatable.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2338380959744
    m_Localized: Once more and I will literally delete your save file and return
      you to the main menu.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3894118629363712
    m_Localized: Oh. My. Why?!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3894214938972160
    m_Localized: That's it, you were amptly warned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3894233238720512
    m_Localized: You have no one to blame but yourself.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3894252410884096
    m_Localized: Bye.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
